msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.ive"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:1 of
msgid "Exponentially scaled modified Bessel function of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类指数缩放修正贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:3 of
msgid "Defined as::"
msgstr "定义为："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:7 of
msgid ""
"For imaginary numbers without a real part, returns the unscaled Bessel "
"function of the first kind `iv`."
msgstr "对于没有实部的虚数，返回第一类未缩放的贝塞尔函数 `iv`。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ive.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:10 of
msgid "Order."
msgstr "阶数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:12 of
msgid "Argument."
msgstr "参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:14 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ive.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:17 of
msgid "Values of the exponentially scaled modified Bessel function."
msgstr "指数缩放修正贝塞尔函数的值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ive.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`iv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:23 of
msgid "Modified Bessel function of the first kind"
msgstr "第一类修正贝塞尔函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`i0e`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:26 of
msgid "Faster implementation of this function for order 0"
msgstr "阶数为 0 时该函数的快速实现"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`i1e`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:29 of
msgid "Faster implementation of this function for order 1"
msgstr "阶数为 1 时该函数的快速实现"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:33 of
msgid ""
"For positive `v`, the AMOS [1]_ `zbesi` routine is called. It uses a "
"power series for small `z`, the asymptotic expansion for large `abs(z)`, "
"the Miller algorithm normalized by the Wronskian and a Neumann series for"
" intermediate magnitudes, and the uniform asymptotic expansions for "
":math:`I_v(z)` and :math:`J_v(z)` for large orders. Backward recurrence "
"is used to generate sequences or reduce orders when necessary."
msgstr ""
"对于正数 `v`，调用 AMOS [1]_ 中的 `zbesi` 程序。它对小 `z` 使用幂级数，对"
"大的 `abs(z)` 使用渐近展开，对中等幅度使用由 Wronskian 归一化的 Miller "
"算法和 Neumann 级数，并对大阶数使用 :math:`I_v(z)` 和 :math:`J_v(z)` 的"
"一致渐近展开。必要时使用向后递推生成序列或降低阶数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:41 of
msgid ""
"The calculations above are done in the right half plane and continued "
"into the left half plane by the formula,"
msgstr "上述计算在右半平面进行，并通过以下公式延拓到左半平面，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:44 of
msgid ""
"I_v(z \\exp(\\pm\\imath\\pi)) = \\exp(\\pm\\pi v) I_v(z)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:46 of
msgid ""
"(valid when the real part of `z` is positive).  For negative `v`, the "
"formula"
msgstr "（当 `z` 的实部为正时有效）。对于负 `v`，使用公式"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:49 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"I_{-v}(z) = I_v(z) + \\frac{2}{\\pi} \\sin(\\pi v) K_v(z)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:51 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`K_v(z)` is the modified Bessel function of the "
"second kind, evaluated using the AMOS routine `zbesk`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`K_v(z)` 是第二类修正贝塞尔函数，使用 AMOS 程序 `zbesk` 进行"
"计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.ive:54 of
msgid ""
"`ive` is useful for large arguments `z`: for these, `iv` easily "
"overflows, while `ive` does not due to the exponential scaling."
msgstr ""
"`ive` 适用于大的 `z` 参数：对于这些值，`iv` 容易溢出，而 `ive` 由于指数"
"缩放不会溢出。"

